Distribution. Europe,
Asia Minor
, Mt. Caucasus, Transcaucasian area, Iran .
Remarks. Mostly collected on flowers of blackberry, but on others as well. The rich catch was also in wine and pitfall traps. Present from plains to mountain areas.
